OL,3,C"Game of Thrones" Actor Michael
OL,4,CPatrick Dies at 35
OL,6,FBelfast actor Michael Campbell has
OL,7,Fdied at the age of 35.
OL,9,FAn online death notice for the actor,
OL,10,Falso known as Michael Patrick, said he
OL,11,Fdied on Tuesday at NI Hospice
OL,12,F"surrounded by his loving family and
OL,13,Ffriends".
OL,15,FThe award-winning actor has worked on
OL,16,Fstage, TV, film and radio productions.
OL,17,FRecent theatre work includes his
OL,18,Fautobiographical play My Right Foot,
OL,19,Fand The Tragedy Of Richard II.
