OL,3,C"Game of Thrones" Actor Michael
OL,4,CPatrick Dies at 35
OL,6,FIn a production where he portrayed
OL,7,FRichard II he picked up The Stage
OL,8,FAwards, Judges Special Award.
OL,10,FOn television, he has appeared in This
OL,11,FTown, Blue Lights, Krypton and Game of
OL,12,FThrones.
OL,14,FHe had been diagnosed with Motor
OL,15,FNeurone Disease in early 2023 and
OL,16,Flater began to use a wheelchair.
OL,18,FIn a social media post, his wife Naomi
OL,19,Fsaid: "Words can't describe how broken-
OL,20,Fhearted we are.
OL,26,@kD@AOUkD@QO]{D@GOU
