OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775913059
OL,3,C"Game of Thrones" Actor Michael
OL,4,CPatrick Dies at 35
OL,6,F"It's been said more than once that
OL,7,FMick was an inspiration to everyone
OL,8,Fwho was privileged enough to come into
OL,9,Fcontact with him, not just in the past
OL,10,Ffew years during his illness but in
OL,11,Fevery day of his life.
OL,13,F"He lived a life as full as any human
OL,14,Fcan live. Joy, abundance of spirit,
OL,15,Finfectious laughter. A titan of a
OL,16,Fginger haired man."
OL,18,FShe added: "We are so grateful for
OL,19,Fevery person who supported us through
OL,20,Fthe last few years."
